summary: AN ORDINANCE vacating the alley in Block 16, Walker's Addition to the City of Seattle, as recorded in Volume 6 of Plats, page 43, Records of King County, Washington, being the alley between 24th Avenue South and 25th Avenue South, from the north margin of South Bayview Street to the northwesterly margin of Rainier Avenue South as established by City of Seattle Condemnation Ordinance 6047 (Clerk File No. 300230).
